reviews: Not very durable, pretty cheap plastic and and it unclips front he top of my Mac a lot. For $20 dollars it does the trick but I’d recommend a more sturdy and durable case to anyone else who’s looking to purchase something that actually will protect their MacBook

Did not work as soon as I plugged it into my early 2015 MacBook. Not worth the money and should’ve read into all the 1 star reviews on this product first. After carefully reading them it seems many people have had damage to their MacBooks after purchasing this item. My Mac was almost 3000, shouldn’t of cheaped out on the cord that’s for sure, advising people to pay the extra cash to get an actual MacBook charger
Amazing product, definitely worth the money, awesome quality
The hat is a very big and thick make and doesn’t fit properly. Almost as if it’s a rip off one of the real brand. Highly disappointed

I bought these cords thinking they would be perfect. They recall that their made for all iPhones above 4s. I have an iPhone 6s and an iPhone 8 and they will not charge either of my phones. For the first few days the battery would drain from my phone as being plugged into these cords. Then they stopped working completely. I do not recommend anybody to buy these, they are a complete waste of money. Go to Apple and buy your cords.
